[h4 id=82World8 
	" 8-2 World 8
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"In this level, always the acceleration at the beginning which saves time. No manipulation of glitches, only reach the end of the level. To avoid a timer that would not finish 3 or 9, I stopped a little at the end to have a time not equivalent to 3 or 9. This stop allowed me to save time and frames otherwise the game would display fireworks for a few seconds.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=83World8 
	" 8-3 World 8
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"At the third level of the last world, always an acceleration that allows you to go faster and save time. NO glitch manipulation but some jumps that can save time. As for the second level of the last world, to avoid the game displays fireworks, I stopped one or two times by jumping slowly which allowed me to have a timer not equivalent to 3 or 9 and to win a few seconds of my movie.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=84World8LastLevel 
	" 8-4 World 8 Last level.
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"For the last level of the game going on in a castle, only one glitch manipulation is done. The manipulation of the glitch is a glitch of the type "wrong warp" which happens towards the end of the level. Always at the beginning the acceleration which saves time also when one leaves a pipe. For the pipe that allows quick access to the end, as for the second level of the world four, I made the invisible block appear to access the pipe and arrive more easily in the game. Just after, I made handling the only glitch in the game. You had to be not too far from the pipe and not too close to the pipe, to be in between to access the water part of the level. The level ends with a fight with bowser and I game is finally over.
	$LF
